      "text": "West Pensacola sits between Perdido Key and downtown, hosting Naval Air Station Pensacola, the National Naval Aviation Museum, and the historic Pensacola Lighthouse.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        1
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
